3OxqWY1Sl_u" data-testid="category-list"><h2 class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo q7Uo5nQcw682PpB8 emZIBXymEFBZt94O">Categories</h2><ul class="U6NNqDwiX4Ic1GSg"><li><a href="/stock-photos/food-and-drink" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food and drink" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food and drink" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food and drink</a></li><li><a href="/stock-photos/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="food" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: food" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">food</a></li><li><a href="/stock-photos/steak-dinner" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Steak Dinner" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Steak Dinner" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Steak Dinner</a></li><li><a href="/photos/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food photos" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food photos" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food photos</a></li><li><a href="/videos/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food videos" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food videos" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food videos</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food illustrations" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food illustrations" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food illustrations</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food designs" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food designs" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food designs</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food drawings" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food drawings" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food drawings</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food backgrounds" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food backgrounds" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food backgrounds</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food icons" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food icons" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food icons</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food silhouettes" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food silhouettes" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food silhouettes</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food clipart" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food clipart" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food clipart</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food symbols" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food symbols" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food symbols</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food borders" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food borders" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food borders</a></li><li><a href="/illustrations/food" class="uYvQ9FNeM4srKxh_ CoMBIA2N74GPYc7o" aria-label="Food patterns" aria-disabled="false" data-trk-action="search_by_category" data-trk-action-context="categoryText: Food patterns" itemType="http://schema.org/relatedLink">Food patterns</a></li></ul></section></div><section class="gxbbT_cgIW4pT0CU IpO2vyKoGz0Khfig HqChtxGsnQm8dsJ7 hT0Teosh5bYan8md H9CGDyOMrboclhb2"><div class="gxbbT_cgIW4pT0CU N2pURkbip2QG3QYE HqChtxGsnQm8dsJ7 hItKYz6uAeEoyFkP"><div data-testid="faq-section" class="gxbbT_cgIW4pT0CU ClpBB3qF6gEpJyEH H9CGDyOMrboclhb2"><div><h2 class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo twLA5FQxKY0woq3p vEVesH3Tyzgpwl7Y">Frequently asked questions</h2><hr class="w49v_3IwxaI_y6gr"/><dl><dt class="my4h6tbr_aUb54DP"><span class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo wMB8HWH8oMs1Xo5t">What&#x27;s a royalty-free license?</span></dt><dd class="OVsPv7uTUMQJcPDt"><div class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo Gj1NQAutdzMpaedF mA1aiDDwHkMyG9JQ"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Royalty-free licenses let you pay once to use copyrighted images and video clips in personal and commercial projects on an ongoing basis without requiring additional payments each time you use that content. It's a win-win, and it's why everything on iStock is only available royalty-free — including all <a href="/photos/food">Food</a> images and footage.</span></div></dd><dt class="my4h6tbr_aUb54DP"><span class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo wMB8HWH8oMs1Xo5t">What kinds of royalty-free files are available on iStock?</span></dt><dd class="OVsPv7uTUMQJcPDt"><div class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo Gj1NQAutdzMpaedF mA1aiDDwHkMyG9JQ"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Royalty-free licenses are the best option for anyone who needs to use stock images commercially, which is why every file on iStock — whether it’s a <a href="/stock-photos">photo</a>, <a href="/stock-illustrations">illustration</a> or <a href="/footage">video clip</a> — is only available royalty-free.</span></div></dd><dt class="my4h6tbr_aUb54DP"><span class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo wMB8HWH8oMs1Xo5t">How can you use royalty-free images and video clips?</span></dt><dd class="OVsPv7uTUMQJcPDt"><div class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo Gj1NQAutdzMpaedF mA1aiDDwHkMyG9JQ"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">From social media ads to billboards, PowerPoint presentations to feature films, you're free to modify, resize and customize every asset on iStock — including all <a href="/photos/food">Food</a> images and footage — to fit your projects. With the exception of "Editorial use only" photos (which can only be used in editorial projects and can't be modified), the possibilities are limitless.</span></div></dd></dl><hr class="nRZYtF6JtIEuPoEc"/></div></div><p data-testid="learn-more-section" class="COaBoshseAYs9tWo q7Uo5nQcw682PpB8 qY3RMWoAc7MC0z2F"><span data-testid="sanitizedString">Learn more about <a href="/royalty-free-images">royalty-free images</a> or view <a href="/faq/using-files#photos">FAQs related to stock photos</a>.</span></p></div></section></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--/$--></div>
